’Щ@039b1db4926ba645eee13e42c7bf2e5a61d2250f37079ae60ceb53644b995b95ЩнTitle: title: export use
Path: Examples
Content:
Re-export a command from another module.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> module spam { export def foo [] { "foo" } }
    module eggs { export use spam foo }
    use eggs foo
    foo

foo

```
